166
00:08:20,997 --> 00:08:23,370
MAX BAKER

167
00:08:24,135 --> 00:08:28,280
THAT'S MINE GRANDCHILD JESSE KIRSHENBAUM.

168
00:08:29,991 --> 00:08:32,415
